Class AbstractPathfindController

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.cshadd.fetch_bot.controllers.AbstractController
      • io.github.cshadd.fetch_bot.controllers.AbstractPathfindController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PathfindControllerImpl

    public abstract class AbstractPathfindController
extends AbstractController
implements PathfindController
    The Class AbstractPathfindController. Defines what a Pathfind Controller is. A Pathfind Controller is basically a manager for pathfinding tasks in Fetch Bot.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Christian Shadd, Maria Verna Aquino, Thanh Vu, Joseph Damian, Giovanni Orozco
